'''NGC 2841''' 是位于[[大熊座|大熊座]]的一个[[螺旋星系|螺旋星系]]。最初认为它距离[[太阳系|太阳系]]大约3000万[[光年|光年]]远，2001年[[天文学家|天文学家]]通过[[哈勃太空望远镜|哈勃太空望远镜]]对该星系的[[造父变星|造父变星]]进行研究确定它的实际距离为14.1[[秒差距|百万秒差距]]（4600万光年）<ref>{{cite journal
  | author      = Macri, L. M.; Stetson, P. B.; Bothun, G. D.; Freedman, W. L.; Garnavich, P. M.; Jha, S.; Madore, B. F.; Richmond, M. W.
  | title       = The Discovery of Cepheids and a New Distance to NGC 2841 Using the Hubble Space Telescope
  | journal     = [[Astrophysical_Journal|Astrophysical Journal]]
  | volume      = 559
  | issue       = 1
  | pages       = 243–259
  | publisher   = [[University_of_Chicago_Press|University of Chicago Press]]
  | issn        = 0004-637X
  | bibcode     = 2001ApJ...559..243M
  | accessdate  = 2009-01-18
  | doi      = 10.1086/322395 |date=September 2001}} </ref>。从结构上看，NGC 2841的最大特征是含有大量年轻的蓝色恒星，而[[电离氢区|电离氢区]]很少<ref>{{cite book
  |first1    = Leonid
  |last1     = Marochnik
  |first2    = Anatoly
  |last2     = Suchkov
  |title     = Milky Way Galaxy
  |edition   = 1st
  |date      = 1995-11-01
  |publisher = [[Routledge|Routledge]]
  |isbn      = 2881249310 
  |page      = 267 }} </ref>。

NGC 2841包含一个[[低电离核发射线区|低电离核发射线区]]（Low-ionization nuclear emission-line region，LINER），这是弱离子原子发射[[谱线|谱线]]区域的特征<ref name="hoetal1997">{{cite journal
